lass=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pregnancy in Prison Campaign<\/h1>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e92754c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e92754c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2504\"><b>Prison is no place to be pregnant.<\/b>\u00a0Level Up campaigns to end the imprisonment of pregnant women and new mothers in England. Evidence shows that pregnancy in prison is inherently unsafe, placing women and babies at serious risk of harm, trauma and death. Through public pressure, legal action and solidarity, we are working to ensure courts stop sending pregnant women to prison and choose safe, community-based alternatives instead.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43f4fe50 elementor-widget elementor-widget-shortcode\" data-id=\"43f4fe50\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"shortcode.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-shortcode\">[petition_block signurl=\"https:\/\/levelup.yourmovement.org\/p\/pregnancy-in-prison\"]<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-09935b5 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"09935b5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78fda3d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"78fda3d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68a1a43 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"68a1a43\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7919dcd elementor-widget__width-auto sub-title elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7919dcd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Aim<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2b10747 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2b10747\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-525f720 elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"525f720\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Let\u2019s end the imprisonment of pregnant women.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-153d6a0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"153d6a0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab5add4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ab5add4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-777781b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"777781b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4cab0d elementor-widget__width-auto sub-title elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b4cab0d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a0735ac e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a0735ac\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e4b3dbe elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e4b3dbe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Prison will never be a safe place to be pregnant. In the past three years, two babies have died when their mothers went into labour inside prison. It\u2019s time to demand an end to the imprisonment of pregnant women and new mothers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15b2e0d4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"15b2e0d4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6231a31f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6231a31f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f70dce9 elementor-widget__width-auto sub-title elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3f70dce9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How the Pregnancy in Prison Campaign began<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-12f53e4f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"12f53e4f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-202723dc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"202723dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In September 2019, Rianna Cleary went into labour alone in her cell inside HMP Bronzefield. She called for help, but nobody came. Prison guards found her the next morning with her dead baby, Aisha, in her arms.<\/p><p>In June 2020, another woman, Louise Powell, went into labour without medical assistance at HMP Styal. Her baby, Brooke, died.<\/p><p>When these harrowing baby deaths broke into the news, the glaring failures of the prison system were stark. Yet there was nobody calling for the obvious: to end the imprisonment for pregnant women. So Level Up set about building a public solidarity movement to demand this.<\/p><p>There\u2019s plenty of evidence that prison is not safe for pregnant women \u2013 for years academics and charities have called for healthcare reforms inside prison \u2013 but no amount of reforms can keep anyone safe when they\u2019re isolated behind locked doors. Our campaign has successfully shifted the discourse away from reform and toward a total end to imprisonment of pregnant women. Step by step, we\u2019re working to end pregnancy in prison.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33ec2176 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"33ec2176\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e4e2290 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6e4e2290\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ef8d68c elementor-widget__width-auto sub-title elementor-widget-tablet__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6ef8d68c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The journey so far<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f151443 e-con-full mobile-archive-section e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3f151443\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a34ab7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"1a34ab7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n  .year-heading{\n  position: sticky;\n  top: 110px;      \/* ajusta: 100\u2013140 seg\u00fan tu header *\/\n  z-index: 9999;\n  background: #0b0b3b;\n  padding: 10px 0;\n}\n\n.year-heading .elementor-heading-title{\n  margin: 0 !important;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 1024px){\n  .year-heading{ top: 44px; }\n}\n<\/style>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6d8c562d e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6d8c562d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-479710fc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"479710fc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2021<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-594e7a3d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"594e7a3d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-249e32c4 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"249e32c4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51128f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"51128f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eddb262 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eddb262\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p><strong>In October 2021,<\/strong>\u00a0when the Prison Ombudsman published its report into the death of Aisha Cleary at HMP Bronzefield, Level Up secured media coverage on the wider issue of pregnancy in prison.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fa3ef72 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fa3ef72\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>Level Up joined forces with women who had been pregnant in prison and charities Birth Companions and Women in Prison to launch a public petition demanding the government put an end to prison sentencing for pregnant women. 12,000 people signed it.<\/p><p>At the same time, the Policing, Crime, Sentencing and Courts Act was going through parliament. Amendments were debated on changes to the sentencing and bail of pregnant women and primary carers, but they didn\u2019t make it into law.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58d7b88 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"58d7b88\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/www.youtube.com\\\/watch?v=m-svZxxLVms&quot;,&quot;show_image_overlay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_overlay&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/welevelup.org\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2025\\\/08\\\/20210619-Level-Up-30479-scaled-e1686745248609-1.webp&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:3710,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;library&quot;},&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-image-overlay lazyload\" style=\"background-image:inherit;\" data-bg-image=\"url(https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/20210619-Level-Up-30479-scaled-e1686745248609-1.webp)\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-custom-embed-play\" role=\"button\" aria-label=\"Play Video\" tabindex=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-eicon-play\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 1000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M838 162C746 71 633 25 500 25 371 25 258 71 163 162 71 254 25 367 25 500 25 633 71 746 163 837 254 929 367 979 500 979 633 979 746 933 838 837 929 746 975 633 975 500 975 367 929 254 838 162M808 192C892 279 933 379 933 500 933 621 892 725 808 808 725 892 621 938 500 938 379 938 279 896 196 808 113 725 67 621 67 500 67 379 108 279 196 192 279 108 383 62 500 62 621 62 721 108 808 192M438 392V642L642 517 438 392Z\"><\/path><\/svg>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66b9f02 e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"66b9f02\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13a30a1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"13a30a1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2022<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a01377f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7a01377f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26a5be2 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"26a5be2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c86dce1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c86dce1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>In January 2022,\u00a0<\/strong>the Prison Ombudsman report into the death of Baby Brooke at HMP Styal in June 2020 was published. Knowing that it would be a distressing day for her mother \u2013 Louise Powell \u2013 Level Up built an online tool for the public to write a message of solidarity to her. 318 people sent heartfelt messages.<\/p><p>A solidarity movement of mums and babies, No Births Behind Bars, was born and staged four<em>\u00a0very cute\u00a0<\/em>protests across the course of the year in order to keep a spotlight on pregnant women in prison, building momentum around the issue. Every time a protest was held, the media covered it, and the Ministry of Justice were asked for comment. This has shown the MoJ that the public do not want to see pregnant women imprisoned:<\/p><p><strong>In March 2022,<\/strong>\u00a0No Births Behind Bars<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2022\/mar\/28\/female-former-inmates-protest-uk-imprisonment-pregnant-women\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0organised the biggest baby protest in history<\/a><\/strong>\u00a0outside Parliament for Mother\u2019s Day 2022.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb55977 e-con-full e-grid e-con e-child\" data-id=\"fb55977\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d79c4b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"4d79c4b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"513\" src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1-768x513.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8753\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1-768x513.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-1.webp 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f17ac6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6f17ac6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"513\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/FREEBABIES3-1-scaled-1-1536x1025-1-768x513.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8754 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/FREEBABIES3-1-scaled-1-1536x1025-1-768x513.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/FREEBABIES3-1-scaled-1-1536x1025-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/FREEBABIES3-1-scaled-1-1536x1025-1-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/FREEBABIES3-1-scaled-1-1536x1025-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/513;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32da041 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"32da041\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In June,<a href=\"https:\/\/www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk\/news\/greater-manchester-news\/prison-never-ever-safe-place-24255509\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0a group of mums and babies demonstrated outside HMP Styal<\/a>\u00a0on the two-year anniversary of the death of Baby Brooke:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b27c47 e-con-full e-grid e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9b27c47\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-016db18 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"016db18\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2-768x512.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8572 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-2.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/512;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f0e467 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2f0e467\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-1-768x512.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8755 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-1-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-3-1.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/512;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc93948 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cc93948\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This was timed with Level Up and No Births Behind Bars\u2019<a href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/NBBB-Letter-to-Sentencing-Council-2309-1.pdf\">\u00a0<strong>open letter to the Sentencing Council and Ministry of Justice<\/strong><\/a><strong>,<\/strong>\u00a0demanding a change to sentencing practices for pregnant women and new mothers. We targeted the Sentencing Council because they oversee court practices \u2013 and it\u2019s the courts that need to stop sending pregnant women to prison in the first place! The letter was launched<a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2022\/sep\/24\/urgent-call-for-review-into-sentencing-pregnant-women-due-to-health-risks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>\u00a0in the Observer<\/strong>.<\/a><\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/nbbb-letter\/\"><strong>The open letter<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0was signed by almost 100 healthcare and legal professionals, including the Royal College of Midwives, Royal College of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists and British Association of Perinatal Medicine. Speaking in support of the campaign, the Royal College of Midwives said<a href=\"https:\/\/www.independent.co.uk\/news\/uk\/home-news\/prison-pregnant-women-babies-deaths-b2175384.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0<strong>\u201cprison is no place for a pregnant woman.\u201d<\/strong><\/a><\/p><p>The Sentencing Council responded to say that they would be evaluating their existing guidance, and would be consulting on whether a separate guideline is needed for pregnant women.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61bf7c98 e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"61bf7c98\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e505785 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7e505785\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2023<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4f1f7a9c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4f1f7a9c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17165bec year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"17165bec\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e271163 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e271163\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>In March 2023<\/strong>, we worked with journalists to uncover new statistics that found women in prison are<a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2023\/mar\/25\/pregnant-women-in-english-jails-are-seven-times-more-likely-to-suffer-stillbirth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0seven times more likely to suffer a stillbirth than women in the general population.<\/a><\/p><p>To draw attention to this, Level Up joined No Births Behind Bars for\u00a0<strong>a Mother\u2019s Day protest<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/metro.co.uk\/2023\/03\/18\/london-protesters-demand-an-end-to-the-imprisonment-of-pregnant-women-18465479\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0outside the Royal Courts of Justice<\/a>\u00a0in London, where the Sentencing Council is based, to sing nursery rhymes and keep up the public pressure on the courts.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-819a9f2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"819a9f2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4-768x512.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8574 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-4.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/512;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7763c2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7763c2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>In May 2023,\u00a0<\/strong>when the Aisha Cleary inquest opened, Level Up supporters sent over 700 messages of solidarity and support to her mother, Rianna Cleary.<\/p><p><strong>In July 2023<\/strong>, the Aisha Cleary\u2019s inquest concluded that \u2018serious failings\u2019 had contributed to her death, and that, if Rianna\u2019s labour had been identified and she had been transferred to hospital,\u00a0<strong>there was an opportunity to take effective steps to ensure Aisha\u2019s survival<\/strong>. Level Up worked with Inquest, a charity specialising in deaths in state custody, to ensure that the press gallery of Surrey Coroner\u2019s Court was full of journalists, and secured national media coverage of this issue ranging from The Times to the Mirror, LBC and Channel 4. At the same time, No Births Behind Bars gathered outside the court to demonstrate public solidarity with Rianna Cleary.<\/p><p><strong>In September 2023<\/strong>, on the four-year anniversary of Aisha Cleary\u2019s death at HMP Bronzefield, Level Up and No Births Behind Bars held a vigil outside the Ministry of Justice to commemorate her death and renew public calls for an end to imprisonment for pregnant women. The cruelties pregnant women face in prison are only possible because they are held from public view \u2013 this is why a public solidarity campaign on the streets is so important for driving change:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca967c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ca967c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"491\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-5-768x491.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8575 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-5-768x491.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-5-300x192.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-5.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/491;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5d2888e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5d2888e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>In September 2023<\/strong>, the campaign also won the support of Seema Misra, the former postmistress who was wrongly convicted in the Post Office scandal and sent to prison while pregnant. In an<a href=\"https:\/\/inews.co.uk\/opinion\/doctors-agree-that-prison-isnt-safe-for-pregnant-women-so-why-are-we-still-locking-them-up-2657607\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0interview with iNews<\/a>, she said \u201cinnocent or not, it is wrong that we send pregnant women to prison\u201d.<\/p><p><strong>In September 2023<\/strong>, the Sentencing Council also opened a public consultation on whether they should introduce a new mitigating factor for pregnancy \u2013 Level Up began work with leading barristers, sentencers and experts to draft a submission and encourage other prominent organisations to do so too.<\/p><p><strong>In October 2023<\/strong>,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/news.sky.com\/story\/should-pregnant-women-be-spared-jail-sentencing-council-reviews-the-impact-of-prison-on-unborn-babies-12991044\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0<strong>Sky News covered the campaign<\/strong><\/a> and included the experiences of women who were pregnant in prison. Level Up also did a live interview with Kay Burley to explain the proposed changes. The Sentencing Council will be sensitive to public opinion regarding a change in sentencing \u2013 so this kind of media coverage was a huge win for the campaign.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d9b8178 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d9b8178\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-6-1536x864-1-768x432.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8576 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-6-1536x864-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-6-1536x864-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-6-1536x864-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-6-1536x864-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/432;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec5261f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ec5261f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bef289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bef289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p><strong>Also in October,<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2023\/oct\/28\/revealed-one-in-three-jailed-pregnant-women-in-england-and-wales-still-to-face-trial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0<strong>The Observer published new statistics<\/strong><\/a>\u00a0showing that\u00a0<strong>one in three pregnant women being held in prison are on remand\u00a0<\/strong>\u2013 meaning they haven\u2019t even been sentenced.<\/p><p><strong>At the end of October 2023<\/strong>, we gathered to chant \u201cNo births behind bars!\u201d as Rianna Cleary walked into Surrey Coroner\u2019s Court to attend the Prevention of Future Deaths (PFD) hearing for her baby, Aisha Cleary. Many from the Level Up community showed up in solidarity with Rianna including Seema Misra.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3362ba1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3362ba1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-1536x1152-1-768x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8577 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-1536x1152-1-768x576.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-1536x1152-1-300x225.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-1536x1152-1-1024x768.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-7-1536x1152-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/576;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-707dda2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"707dda2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bef289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bef289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p><strong>In November 2023<\/strong>, the coroner ultimately\u00a0<strong>decided not to issue a Preventing Future Deaths report<\/strong>, concluding that sufficient changes had been made. Following the decision,\u00a0<strong>Rianna Cleary<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/Czo6jgyoHtF\/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&amp;igshid=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0<strong>read her statement on Channel 4 News<\/strong><\/a>, underscoring the potentially limited impact of the changes that have been made, and\u00a0<strong>announcing her support of Level Up\u2019s campaign<\/strong>.<\/p><p>This is the first time she has spoken out publicly since Aisha\u2019s death. She said, \u201cwhen it comes to prisons, what\u2019s written on a piece of paper is never what happens in practice. The way the prisons are run, it is all about\u00a0<strong>power and control<\/strong>. They will never be caring places. Prison officers do not always follow policy \u2013 look what happened to me when I pressed my cell bell twice \u2013\u00a0<strong>nobody came<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc2b66a e-con-full e-grid e-con e-child\" data-id=\"fc2b66a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb44ddd elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fb44ddd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"458\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-8-1-768x458.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8578 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-8-1-768x458.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-8-1-300x179.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-8-1.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/458;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c44a4f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"7c44a4f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"480\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-9-768x480.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8579 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-9-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-9-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-9.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/480;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4367b24 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4367b24\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bef289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bef289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>Level Up co-director Janey\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.channel4.com\/news\/end-imprisonment-of-pregnant-women-so-no-more-babies-die-says-gender-justice-campaigner\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">was also on Channel 4 that day,<\/a>\u00a0reiterating that no amount of reforms will be enough,\u00a0<strong>the only way another baby death can be prevented is to stop sending pregnant women to prison<\/strong>. She said: \u201cMedical professionals agree it will never be safe, yet there have been no changes to the court system, so what we need are new measures put in place to ensure that courts are not sending pregnant women to prison. Several countries have stopped sending pregnant women to prison, and we need to become one of them.\u201d<\/p><p><strong>Media momentum around the campaign picked up pace. Later in November,<\/strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.bbc.co.uk\/iplayer\/episode\/m001sp4b\/politics-london-19112023\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BBC Politics<\/a>\u00a0covered pregnancy in prison and Sir Bob Neill MP, Chair of the Justice Select Committee, announced his support for a stronger sentencing framework to prevent pregnant women going to prison. Also on the programme was midwifery lecturer and campaign supporter Maria Garcia De Frutos, and Ellie Reeves MP (former Shadow Prisons Minister). All agreed that alternatives to prison for pregnant women were needed.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-432b47a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"432b47a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"433\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-10-768x433.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8580 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-10-768x433.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-10-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-10.webp 1024w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/433;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a0d65a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2a0d65a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bef289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bef289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p><strong>At the end of November 2023,\u00a0<\/strong>alongside lawyers, academics, psychiatrists and organisations, Level Up submitted a response to the Sentencing Council\u2019s consultation on a new mitigating factor for pregnancy.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8f628b elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"e8f628b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2SC-Consultation-2023-Level-Up-submission-FINAL.docx-1-1.pdf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Read Level Up\u2019s submission to the Sentencing Council<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0ec515 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d0ec515\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bef289 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5bef289\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p>As the Sentencing Council\u2019s first consultation closed, they put forward even stronger proposals to change the sentencing of pregnant women, including measures that instruct courts to \u201cavoid the possibility of an offender giving birth in prison\u201d \u2013 these measures, if brought into place, will mark a huge victory for the campaign. Level Up is currently coordinating our response.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3480f8b e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3480f8b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9483b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c9483b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2024<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a9ec9f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8a9ec9f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-908c0f9 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"908c0f9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e3b199c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e3b199c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In January 2024, Level Up kicked off the year with a huge campaign victory: we helped secure a landmark judgment where the Court of Appeal overturned a heavily pregnant woman\u2019s prison sentence and replaced it with a suspended sentence on the basis of risks to her pregnancy.<\/p><p>The woman\u2019s mother had reached out to Level Up in 2023, we found top lawyers to appeal her sentence and test a legal argument on mandatory minimum sentences. Not only was she released from prison the same day, the case established a legal precedent, where pregnancy can contribute to \u201cexceptional circumstances\u201d that make a mandatory minimum sentence disproportionate.\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2024\/jan\/19\/pregnant-woman-jail-sentence-quashed-in-landmark-uk-ruling\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Read more about the case in the Guardian here.<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong>In February 2024,<\/strong>\u00a0in coalition with leading lawyers and academics, Level Up submitted our response to the Sentencing Council\u2019s consultation on the revised Imposition of Custodial and Community Sentences guideline. We also worked behind the scenes to rally lots of supportive expert submissions to the consultation, including from psychiatrists and psychologists.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9488fbf elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"9488fbf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/2SC-Consultation-2023-Level-Up-submission-FINAL.docx-1-1.pdf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Read Level Up\u2019s submission to the Sentencing Council<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bafd0f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6bafd0f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Level Up also conducted public polling with women\u2019s charity One Small Thing, which found that<strong>\u00a0the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/society\/2024\/feb\/24\/pregnant-women-and-new-mothers-shouldnt-be-sent-to-jail-uk-public-says\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">majority of the public support sentencing reform for pregnant women and mothers.<\/a><\/strong><\/p><p><strong>In March 2024,<\/strong>\u00a0Level Up joined No Births Behind Bars once more for our third Mother\u2019s Day protest outside the Royal Courts of Justice to demand the Sentencing Council take action to stop courts sending pregnant women to prison.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-572b897 e-con-full e-grid e-con e-child\" data-id=\"572b897\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af5ccd8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"af5ccd8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"578\" height=\"489\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-11.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8581 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-11.webp 578w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-11-300x254.webp 300w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 578px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 578\/489;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0786ae5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"0786ae5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-12-1536x1024-1-768x512.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8582 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-12-1536x1024-1-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-12-1536x1024-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-12-1536x1024-1-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-12-1536x1024-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/512;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b417c1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b417c1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>It is clear that, in the past four years, Level Up have managed to shift the Overton window regarding imprisonment of pregnant women. Our media strategy, lobbying of the Sentencing Council and protests with No Births Behind Bars have successfully turned the dial away from healthcare reform inside prison toward an end to prison for pregnant women \u2013\u2013 support for the campaign is picking up pace and our demand has become a regular media talking point.<\/p><p>In\u00a0<strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">April 2024<\/strong>, the Sentencing Council introduced a new mitigating factor for pregnancy in prison sentencing. Courts now have to consider the impact that prison could have on a pregnant woman, and the fact that every pregnancy in prison is high risk. It\u2019s a huge campaign victory \u2013\u2013 and the Sentencing Council even acknowledged Level Up\u2019s submissions in their formal response!<\/p><p>In response to the news,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/law\/2024\/mar\/18\/woman-baby-stillborn-hmp-styal-prison-sentencing-guidance\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-stringify-link=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/law\/2024\/mar\/18\/woman-baby-stillborn-hmp-styal-prison-sentencing-guidance\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\">Louise Powell, whose baby Brooke died at HMP Styal in 2020<\/a>, said:\u00a0<em data-stringify-type=\"italic\">\u201cI hope that the changes to guidance mean fewer pregnant women are sent to prison, if not there is a real risk that women in labour will be left begging for help the way I was and will pay the ultimate price. If my daughter Brooke had been born in the community she would be here today. No woman should have to give birth behind bars.\u201d<\/em><\/p><p>In\u00a0<strong>September 2024,\u00a0<\/strong>Level Up launched a legal toolkit:\u00a0<em>Representing pregnant women and mothers in the criminal justice system.\u00a0<\/em>Written by three Doughty Street Chambers barristers, Maya Sikand KC, Pippa Woodrow and Hannah Smith, and Level Up co-director Janey Starling (pictured below), the toolkit is designed to equip lawyers with the key arguments, resources and tools to represent pregnant women at all stages of the criminal justice process.<\/p><p>We launched the toolkit with a sold-out event at Doughty Street Chambers on 5 September 2024.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fff2639 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fff2639\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-13-1536x863-1-1024x575.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-8583 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-13-1536x863-1-1024x575.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-13-1536x863-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-13-1536x863-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-13-1536x863-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/449;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-983ebff elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"983ebff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/piptoolkit.squarespace.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Access the legal toolkit<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-243045c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"243045c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In\u00a0<strong>December 2024,\u00a0<\/strong>the government opened an Independent Sentencing Review, which called for evidence on changes to sentencing that would better meet the needs of different victims and offenders. Working with a team of expert lawyers and women who experienced pregnancy in prison, we submitted 23 pages of evidence on why pregnant women should not be sent to prison.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-45cab02 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"45cab02\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Level-Up-Sentencing-Review-submission-2024-1-1.pdf\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Read our response to the 2024\/5 Sentencing Review<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a2c988 e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0a2c988\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-079f063 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"079f063\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2025<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c2acf47 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c2acf47\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59edb2b year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"59edb2b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-255d532 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"255d532\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In\u00a0<strong>January 2025,\u00a0<\/strong>EastEnders showed a key storyline that featured long-time character Sonia Fowler pregnant in prison. She quoted Level Up\u2019s statistics that pregnant women in prison are twice as likely to suffer a premature birth!<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ebc1879 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ebc1879\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-14-1-300x168.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-8584 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-14-1-300x168.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-14-1-1024x573.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-14-1-768x430.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-14-1.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 300px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 300\/168;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-660ef95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"660ef95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Given that EastEnders has 5 million viewers per evening, it was an incredible indication that the campaign has now cut through into mainstream pop culture, which is always a litmus test for zeitgeist social issues. Working with a woman who we co-founded the campaign with, Level Up secured a first-person piece in the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/metro.co.uk\/2025\/01\/22\/like-eastenders-sonia-prison-pregnant-dehumanising-22394436\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Metro<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong>about her experiences of pregnancy in prison, and protest group No Births Behind Bars created an adorable\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/reel\/DE7eUSyIR8h\/?igsh=MWFhNnprZzA3bGZweg==\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u2018Free Sonia\u2019 video<\/a>:<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-056a455 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"056a455\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-15-225x300.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-8585 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-15-225x300.webp 225w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-15-768x1024.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-15.webp 1152w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 225px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 225\/300;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7cb7e49 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7cb7e49\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In\u00a0<strong>February 2025,\u00a0<\/strong>harrowing stories of women at HMP Bronzefield being unlawfully handcuffed to male officers during childbirth emerged in a\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.channel4.com\/news\/exclusive-pregnant-prisoners-forced-to-wear-handcuffs-in-labour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Channel 4 report<\/strong><\/a>, which also featured Level Up co-director Janey. The two women, who were cuffed to officers for 34 and 48 hours respectively, demanded an independent investigation into how this was allowed to happen. Immediately, the Level Up community sprang into action to support them: using our\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/inquiry\">web tool<\/a>, over 200 people emailed the Ministry of Justice to echo their calls for an investigation. At the same time, No Births Behind Bars held a baby protest outside the Ministry of Justice:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-295703a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"295703a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"512\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-16-768x512.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8586 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-16-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-16-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-16-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-16.webp 1536w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/512;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-075d9ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"075d9ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In\u00a0<strong>March 2025,\u00a0<\/strong>the campaign secured a huge victory. The Sentencing Council announced their new Imposition of community and custodial sentences guideline, which included a swathe of hard-won sentencing changes for pregnant women. The new guideline acknowledges the risks that pregnant women face in prison and directs courts to\u00a0<em>\u201cavoid the possibility of an offender navigating the risks associated with pregnancy, birth and the postnatal period (up to 12 months after birth) in custody.\u201d\u00a0<\/em><\/p><p>The guideline also acknowledges Level Up\u2019s contributions to shaping it, as well as the new case law that we helped to produce.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4eaed3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c4eaed3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17-300x298.webp\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-8587 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17-300x298.webp 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17-1024x1018.webp 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17-150x150.webp 150w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17-768x764.webp 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/image-17.webp 1088w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 300px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 300\/298;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6620c86 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6620c86\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>In April 2025,<\/b>\u00a0the campaign hit a roadblock when the Justice Secretary Shabana Mahmood\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.theguardian.com\/commentisfree\/2025\/apr\/01\/labour-prison-reform-justice-system\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">blocked the new guideline from coming into effect after it was criticised by the far-right.<\/a>\u00a0<\/p><p>The Sentencing Council, who had been browbeaten by the government, was forced to suspend the new guideline while the government passed emergency legislation to prevent the guidelines directing courts to obtain pre-sentence reports for specific groups, including pregnant women and mothers. It was extremely frustrating to see pregnant women caught up in the crosshairs of populist culture wars.<\/p><p>In response,\u00a0<b>900 Level Up supporters<\/b>\u00a0emailed Shabana Mahmood urging her not to remove protections for pregnant women. Nadia Whittome MP raised a parliamentary question and, when the government\u2019s new emergency legislation was being debated in the House of Lords, Level Up worked closely with Bishop Rachel Treweek to put forward amendments to try and save the guidelines.\u00a0<\/p><p>We put up a really good fight, but the government rejected the amendments \u2013 and we learned a valuable lesson about how fragile feminist victories are within a populist political landscape.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3fab229 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3fab229\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.38.29-768x432.png\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8588 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.38.29-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.38.29-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.38.29-1024x577.png 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.38.29.png 1332w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/432;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ed999c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ed999c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In\u00a0<b>May 2025,\u00a0<\/b>the Independent Sentencing Review recommended that the government prioritises comm$unity alternatives and deferred sentences for pregnant women and mothers, adding to the widespread consensus that prison is simply no place for pregnant women and mothers.<\/p><p>In\u00a0<b>June 2025,\u00a0<\/b>\u00a0Level Up and No Births Behind Bars jointly won \u2018campaign of the year\u2019 award at the SMK Campaigner Awards 2025! This was a huge recognition of how much work had gone into this.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9a986a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9a986a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"511\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.39.39-768x511.png\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8589 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.39.39-768x511.png 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.39.39-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.39.39-1024x682.png 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.39.39.png 1328w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/511;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0478c94 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0478c94\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Later in\u00a0<b>June,\u00a0<\/b>the government finally agreed to commission an independent investigation into the use of restraints on pregnant women in prison.<\/p><p><b>In September 2025,\u00a0<\/b>the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/sentencingcouncil.org.uk\/guidelines\/imposition-of-community-and-custodial-sentences-effective-from-1-september-2025\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">new Sentencing Guideline<\/a>\u00a0that directs courts to avoid sentencing pregnant women to prison finally came into effect.<\/p><p><b>In December 2025,<\/b>\u00a0the government still had not begun their independent investigation into the use of restraints on pregnant women, so No Births Behind Bars hosted a nativity-themed demonstration outside the Ministry of Justice and delivered Lord Timpson a giant Christmas card. Within an hour, the government had confirmed that they would send over their draft terms of reference to lawyers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb4f1fa e-con-full e-grid e-con e-child\" data-id=\"eb4f1fa\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3356d6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a3356d6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"577\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.33-768x577.png\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8590 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.33-768x577.png 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.33-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.33-1024x769.png 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.33.png 1214w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/577;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1941923 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1941923\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"558\" data-src=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.57-768x558.png\" class=\"attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-image-8591 lazyload\" alt=\"\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.57-768x558.png 768w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.57-300x218.png 300w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.57-1024x744.png 1024w, https:\/\/welevelup.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Captura-de-pantalla-2026-01-29-a-las-18.41.57.png 1192w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" src=\"data:image\/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxIiB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciPjwvc3ZnPg==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 768px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 768\/558;\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-242ec38 e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"242ec38\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e880544 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e880544\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2026<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da28dff e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"da28dff\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e4b188 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2e4b188\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d78f990 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d78f990\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"p1\"><b>In January 2026,\u00a0<\/b>we achieved a huge campaign victory. The government passed the Sentencing Act, which included an amendment to the Bail Act 1976 that says courts must consider a woman\u2019s pregnancy or whether she is a primary carer when making a decision on whether to grant her bail. This was the second core demand of our campaign!<\/p><p class=\"p1\">This means that our campaign has technically secured all that it set out to: changing the way that courts respond to pregnant women and mothers.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d8232f e-con-full year-heading e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3d8232f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67b1519 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"67b1519\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:44,&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;,&quot;mobile&quot;],&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What next?<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0b90af e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e0b90af\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-751c142 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"751c142\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ed0f63 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8ed0f63\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eddb262 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eddb262\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"><p class=\"p1\">After five years, our campaign has achieved its original goals of changing the sentencing guidelines and bail process for pregnant women and mothers. This has been achieved through precision, persistence and creating political and cultural pressure through a constellation of people and organisations.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Now the challenge remains to ensure these changes are implemented in practice, to keep pregnant women and mothers caught up in the criminal legal system out of prison.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">The final step will be for the government to legislate against the imprisonment of pregnant women completely, which will remove a court\u2019s powers to send a pregnant woman to prison outright.<\/p><p class=\"p1\">Latest Ministry of Justice figures show that there were 196 pregnant women in prison in 2024\/5 with\u00a042 births to women in prison. <b>This is a drop in numbers from the previous year, and for the first time since records began, there were no births behind bars. All women made it to hospital in time.<\/b><\/p><p class=\"p1\">Level Up will keep campaigning on this issue until courts stop sending pregnant women to prison. Eleven countries, including Mexico and Brazil, have laws against sending pregnant women to prison.\u00a0There is nothing stopping England from doing the same.\u00a0<\/p><p class=\"p1\"><strong>Let\u2019s put an end to pregnancy in prison.<\/strong><\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e56516c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e56516c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7d5c907 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7d5c907\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-773bb86 year-group e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"773bb86\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be0afd7 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"be0afd7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/welevelup.org\/donate\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Donate<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5436630 elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"5436630\" data-element_type=\"widget\" d